# PalJS Project Overview

PalJS is a toolkit for building NodeJS, Prisma, GraphQL, and React applications. It provides a set of packages that help with various aspects of development.

## Key Resources
- The [package.json](mdc:package.json) contains the main project configuration and scripts
- The [README.md](mdc:README.md) provides an overview of the project and quick start guide
- The project is structured as a monorepo with packages in the [packages/](mdc:packages) directory

## Build Configuration
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) - TypeScript configuration
- [tsconfig.build.bundle.json](mdc:tsconfig.build.bundle.json) - Build configuration for bundles
- [tsconfig.build.regular.json](mdc:tsconfig.build.regular.json) - Regular build configuration
